# Date: 2026-03-10 | Agent: Claude Code
#
# Base config — applied to ALL targets.
# Board-specific overrides live in sdkconfig.defaults.<target>.
# Set target with: idf.py set-target <esp32|esp32s3|esp32c6|esp32c5>
